item.title: CVE-2019-5088|2024-08-04T19:47:56.667Z -- investintech.com%20inc. -- able2extract%20professional
item.description: An exploitable memory corruption vulnerability exists in Investintech Able2Extract Professional 14.0.7 x64. A specially crafted BMP file can cause an out-of-bounds memory write, allowing a potential attacker to execute arbitrary code on the victim machine. Can trigger this vulnerability by sending the user a specially crafted BMP file.
